===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|slight||}}
# To treat as slight or not worthy of attention, to make light of.
# To treat with [[disdain]] or [[neglect]].
# To act [[negligently]] or [[carelessly]].
# To overthrow; to demolish.
# To make even or level.
# To throw heedlessly.

